OL,3,CMum with incurable skin cancer calls
OL,4,Con next UK Government to help more
OL,5,Clives
OL,7,FA mum from Dudley who had to quit her
OL,8,Fbusiness after finding out she had
OL,9,Fincurable skin cancer has called on
OL,10,Fthe next UK Government to help save
OL,11,Fmore lives.
OL,13,FHelen Hickman was shocked to discover
OL,14,Fthat a tiny blood-blister on her arm
OL,15,Fwas in fact melanoma in March 2021.
OL,17,FDoctors believed surgery had cleared
OL,18,Fthe cancer but, less than a year
OL,19,Flater, Helen was given the devastating
OL,20,Fnews that it had spread to her abdomen
OL,21,Fand her lungs.
