OL,7,FFrom an active person who'd just
OL,8,Fstarted a new business, Helen has
OL,9,Fsince found herself back and forth
OL,10,Fbetween hospitals, her body weakened
OL,11,Fby surgery and treatment.
OL,13,FShe wants to see a future Government
OL,14,Finvest more into cancer research as
OL,15,Fwell as tackle delays.
OL,17,FShe was forced to wait months for
OL,18,Ftreatment, despite her oncologist
OL,19,Fsuggesting it should start early.
