OL,7,FHelen said: "In December he said by
OL,8,Fthe beginning of February he wanted me
OL,9,Fon my treatment.
OL,11,F"He wanted to start the treatment. It
OL,12,Fwas April when I finally started my
OL,13,Ftreatment with all the messing about
OL,14,Fand to-ing and fro-ing.
OL,16,F"So I think more needs to be done,
OL,17,Fmore time, more experts need to be
OL,18,Finvolved. It does need to be faster."
