OL,7,FThat is something that's echoed by
OL,8,FCancer Research UK, who say thousands
OL,9,Fof lives could be saved if research
OL,10,Finto the disease was prioritised.
OL,12,FHelen's cancer is now incurable and
OL,13,Fshe doesn't know how long she has left.
OL,15,FShe says she can only hope that more
OL,16,Finvestment, leads to more options for
OL,17,Ftreatment, and a chance to prolong her
OL,18,Flife.
OL,20,FWhat are all the parties pledging to
OL,21,Fdo to help people affected by cancer?
